              <DefinitionShort>to cease one’s work or activity, resulting in a period of rest</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to rest</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to cease from work</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>{L:καταπαύω&lt;SDBG:καταπαύω:000000&gt;}[a] and κατάπαυσις appear to differ in meaning from ἀναπαύομαι[a] and {L:ἀνάπαυσις&lt;SDBG:ἀνάπαυσις:000001&gt;}[b] ({D:23.80}) in that the emphasis of {L:καταπαύω&lt;SDBG:καταπαύω:000000&gt;}[a] and κατάπαυσις is more upon the cessation of activity resulting in rest rather than upon the mere restorative character of rest.</Comments>
